{"id": 1476, "genre": 1001, "title": "你有什么日常的雄心伟略？", "description": "日常的最终命运都以半道崩殂而告终的雄心伟略，多到论斤卖啊我。（题图来自：Nicolet Schenck）", "record_count": 5224, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170125113335O9NIbEy1MQR4ptYT.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-02-04T17:00:26Z", "options": [{"id": 161792, "content": "我能放下手机一小时", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 924661}, {"id": 162048, "content": "明天早起锻炼！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 124192}, {"id": 162304, "content": "多看书 少睡觉", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 926130}, {"id": 166912, "content": "在假期开头就gang完作业", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 800990}, {"id": 161793, "content": "给我半年可以练成彭于晏的身材.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925327}, {"id": 175873, "content": "我只想改变改变自己的性格。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1021482}, {"id": 161794, "content": "自学英语四年，减肥健身五年，仍然收获abandon和一肚子赘肉", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925330}, {"id": 162050, "content": "从早学到晚，但实际上是从早闲到晚", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795994}, {"id": 162306, "content": "今晚挑灯夜读！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889095}, {"id": 161795, "content": "放假之前认真的写了假期安排和计划", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 895868}, {"id": 162307, "content": "我偷偷立了flag，劳资要考研！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 909727}, {"id": 161796, "content": "找到一份合适的工作！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925338}, {"id": 162052, "content": "沉迷学习无法自拔。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 844558}, {"id": 162564, "content": "作业！！我还有